data.description: Beautiful, 3 BR, 2.5 BA corner unit town home convenient to schools, transportation, highways, shopping and restaurants. Recently updated and move in ready, it features a spacious and light filled living room with view to the kitchen and private back yard, dining area, luxury lvp floors, neutral paint. Vaulted ceiling in master. Very affordable HOA, renders it attractive for both owner occupants and investors. Property available to show beginning afternoon Feb 10.
